{
	"info": {
		"name": "Events API",
		"description": "## Microservicio events\n\nPlataforma de reserva de entradas para eventos con autenticación AWS Cognito.\n\n### 🔑 Obtener token de acceso\n\n1. **Regístrate/Inicia sesión** en la Hosted UI de Cognito:\n   ```\n   https://us-east-1yzwnali2a.auth.us-east-1.amazoncognito.com/login?client_id=3gv2oqe4niko3s47srn1kitsk6&response_type=code&scope=email+openid+phone&redirect_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fd84l1y8p4kdic.cloudfront.net\n   ```\n\n2. Copia el parámetro `code` de la URL de redirección después del login.\n\n3. Usa el request **Cognito - Get Token** para canjear el código por un `access_token`.\n\n4. Copia el `access_token` en la variable de colección `access_token`.\n\n### 📋 Endpoints\n\n| Método | Ruta | Acceso |\n|--------|------|--------|\n| GET | /api/events | 🔓 Público |\n| GET | /api/events/{id} | 🔓 Público |\n| POST | /api/events | 🔒 Privado |\n| POST | /api/attendees | 🔒 Privado |\n| POST | /api/reservations | 🔒 Privado |\n| PUT | /api/reservations/{id}/cancel | 🔒 Privado |\n| GET | /api/reservations | 🔒 Privado |",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
	},
	"variable": [
		{
			"key": "base_url",
			"value": "http://localhost:8080",
			"type": "string"
		},
		{
			"key": "access_token",
			"value": "",
			"type": "string"
		},
		{
			"key": "event_id",
			"value": "1",
			"type": "string"
		},
		{
			"key": "reservation_id",
			"value": "1",
			"type": "string"
		},
		{
			"key": "cognito_code",
			"value": "",
			"type": "string"
		},
		{
			"key": "cognito_domain",
			"value": "https://us-east-1yzwnali2a.auth.us-east-1.amazoncognito.com",
			"type": "string"
		},
		{
			"key": "client_id",
			"value": "3gv2oqe4niko3s47srn1kitsk6",
			"type": "string"
		},
		{
			"key": "client_secret",
			"value": "14qdd388f1j6fge52el3l5r2ouvcg5sperlno3701t2jj1chgeiu",
			"type": "string"
		},
		{
			"key": "redirect_uri",
			"value": "https://d84l1y8p4kdic.cloudfront.net",
			"type": "string"
		}
	],
	"item": [
		{
			"name": "🔑 Autenticación",
			"description": "Flujo para obtener el token de acceso de AWS Cognito.",
			"item": [
				{
					"name": "🔗 Hosted UI (Login/Register)",
					"request": {
						"method": "GET",
						"header": [],
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{cognito_domain}}/login?client_id={{client_id}}&response_type=code&scope=email+openid+phone&redirect_uri={{redirect_uri}}",
							"host": ["{{cognito_domain}}"],
							"path": ["login"],
							"query": [
								{
									"key": "client_id",
									"value": "{{client_id}}"
								},
								{
									"key": "response_type",
									"value": "code"
								},
								{
									"key": "scope",
									"value": "email openid phone"
								},
								{
									"key": "redirect_uri",
									"value": "{{redirect_uri}}"
								}
							]
						}
					}
				},
				{
					"name": "Cognito - Get Token",
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"exec": [
									"var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
									"if (jsonData.access_token) {",
									"    pm.collectionVariables.set('access_token', jsonData.access_token);",
									"    console.log('Token de acceso guardado exitosamente');",
									"}"
								],
								"type": "text/javascript"
							}
						}
					],
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Content-Type",
								"value": "application/x-www-form-urlencoded"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "urlencoded",
							"urlencoded": [
								{
									"key": "grant_type",
									"value": "authorization_code",
									"type": "text"
								},
								{
									"key": "client_id",
									"value": "{{client_id}}",
									"type": "text"
								},
								{
									"key": "client_secret",
									"value": "{{client_secret}}",
									"type": "text"
								},
								{
									"key": "code",
									"value": "{{cognito_code}}",
									"description": "Copia aquí el código que obtuviste de la URL de redirección después del login en la Hosted UI",
									"type": "text"
								},
								{
									"key": "redirect_uri",
									"value": "{{redirect_uri}}",
									"type": "text"
								}
							]
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{cognito_domain}}/oauth2/token",
							"host": ["{{cognito_domain}}"],
							"path": ["oauth2", "token"]
						},
						"description": "Canjea el authorization_code por un access_token.\n\n1. Abre el request 🔗 Hosted UI, regístrate/inicia sesión\n2. Copia el parámetro `code` de la URL de redirección\n3. Pégalo en la variable `cognito_code`\n4. Ejecuta este request\n5. El token se guarda automáticamente en la variable `access_token`"
					}
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"name": "🔓 Públicos",
